data.description: Uncover the potential in this charming home! Situated on .47 acres, it boasts an open family room/kitchen with walkout to the rear deck perfect for entertaining! Kitchen features wood cabinets, granite countertops and SS appliances. The spacious primary bedroom offers a large walk-in closet, and en suite with a garden tub and shower.  The lower level is a blank canvas for you to create a lower level of your dreams! *Roof 18' *A/C & Heat pump 20' *HWH 17' *Driveway 13' *Gutter guards  Property being sold AS IS
